<h1><code ng:non-bindable="">jqmLiLink</code>
<div><span class="hint">directive in module <code ng:non-bindable="">jqm</code>
</span>
</div>
</h1>
<div><h2 id="description">Description</h2>
<div class="description"><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmlilink-page"><p>Creates a jquery mobile list item link entry.</p>
<p>Must be inside of a <a href="#/api/jqm.directive:jqmListview">jqmListview</a></p>
<ul>
<li>Add a <code>&lt;img jqm-li-thumb&gt;</code> inside for a thumbnail.</li>
<li>Add a <code>&lt;span jqm-li-count&gt;</code> inside for a count.</li>
</ul>
</div></div>
<h2 id="usage">Usage</h2>
<div class="usage">as attribute<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&lt;ANY jqm-li-link
     [jqm-li-l-ink="{string}"]
     [icon="{string}"]
     [iconpos="{string}"]
     [icon-shadow="{string}"]&gt;
   ...
&lt;/ANY&gt;</pre>
<h4 id="usage_parameters">Parameters</h4><table class="variables-matrix table table-bordered table-striped"><thead><tr><th>Param</th><th>Type</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>jqmLiLInk <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-string">string</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmlilink-page"><p>The link, or href, that this listitem should go to when clicked.</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>icon <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-string">string</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmlilink-page"><p>What icon to use for the link.  Default &#39;ui-icon-arrow-r&#39;.</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>iconpos <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-string">string</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmlilink-page"><p>Where to put the icon. Default &#39;right&#39;.</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>iconShadow <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-string">string</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmlilink-page"><p>Whether the icon should have a shadow or not. Default true.</p>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
</div>
